main.description: NFTflow is a platform for creating liquid markets for illiquid Non-Fungible Tokens (NFTs) on StarkNet
main.bio: StarkNet is a permissionless decentralized ZK-Rollup. It operates as an L2 network over Ethereum, enabling any dApp to achieve unlimited scale for its computation â€“ without compromising Ethereum's composability and security.

education.description: Alex is the founder and lead contributor to NFTflow which is NFT liquidity protocol and decentralised NFT exchange.Alex dove deep into crypto in 2017 after discovering Ethereum and was attracted to it by the idea it could become this alternative financial system and economy.It wasn't until the winter of 2021, after Alex was exploring and investing in the NFT ecosystem, that he decided to create NFTflow because of the clear liquidity issues he was experiencing.Initially Created as a protocol to create cryptocurrency that was backed by NFTs, NFTX has evolved from offering NFT index funds to a full blown NFT DEX.
